{"body": "The capital of an applicant, calculated in accordance with this Part, is to be treated as if it were a weekly income of\u2014\n\u00a31 for each \u00a3500 in excess of \u00a310,000 but not exceeding \u00a316,000; and\n\u00a31 for any excess which is not a complete \u00a3500.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 1 para. 37", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/1/paragraph/37", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-06-07-uk-ctr-england-pensioner-sch1-p37", "heading": "Schedule 1 paragraph 37 - Calculation of tariff income from capital", "id": "cbbcf7f2-da5b-5cd0-b617-3f511cd3d4bf", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "2885", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "schedule/1/paragraph/37", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2012"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "paragraph", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 1 para. 37", "level": 2, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W"], "references_to": ["uksi/2012/2885", "ukia/2012/413"], "retrieved_at": null, "schedule": "1"}, "ordinal": 37, "parent_citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/1", "parent_id": "8700cbcf-aa0a-583b-be74-4116beec03c0", "source_as_of": "2026-06-07-uk-ctr-england-pensioner-sch1-p37", "source_document_id": "uksi/2012/2885", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/1/paragraph/37", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-06-07-uk-ctr-england-pensioner-sch1-p37/uksi/2012/2885/schedule-1-paragraph-37.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/1/paragraph/37", "version": "2026-06-07-uk-ctr-england-pensioner-sch1-p37"}
